aboutUs: At Brook Investment Properties / Remodeling, we are a team of highly skilled and experienced professionals dedicated to providing top-notch plumbing and remodeling services to homeowners and businesses throughout Alabama. Our local expertise and commitment to excellence ensure that every project we undertake is completed with precision, efficiency, and a keen eye for detail.

whyChooseUs.mainPitch: Experience the peace of mind that comes with choosing a trusted local plumbing and remodeling company with a proven track record of delivering exceptional results.
sellingPoints: Fully licensed and insured professionals with extensive knowledge of local building codes and regulations.
Comprehensive range of services, from routine plumbing repairs to complete bathroom and kitchen remodels.
Unwavering commitment to using high-quality materials and implementing industry-leading techniques for long-lasting solutions.

googleReviewsBySlug.json.text: I recently was in the process of getting my home refinanced and had to have some repairs done. I googled and talked to several other contractors that set dates and times and didn't even bother to show up. I called Brook Investment Properties and Mike showed up the same day gave me a quote and had the work done the next day. He is my go to for any of my home repairs

googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: John Garrett Yuhas
googleReviewsBySlug.json.text:
This is one of the most professional companies I’ve worked with in a long time

For the last year I have been trying to get a handyman out to my house to do some small projects. I had some rotten wood, some painting, etc.

I couldn’t get anyone to come out, nor could I get anyone to give me a quote or even return a phone call

They go above and beyond and exhibit extreme professionalism and courtesy

Something you don’t see anymore

I really appreciated them going above and beyond on my house project.

I had cut a cable wire behind the house

And they ended up having to stay three hours late to fix it in the dark with flashlights,

And they did not have to fix my mistake.

That is professionalism Defined

I will be using them again in the future and I really appreciate y’all Brooke investment !
